587
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:51,680
But not professionally.

588
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:53,450
These are separate issues.

589
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:54,560
No, you...

590
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:57,220
How can you apologize to such a beast?

591
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:59,460
Do you have any principles at all?

592
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,560
Such a child.

593
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:03,440
Huaming, Huaming.

594
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:05,370
[Reading Zhu Baiqing's classics]

595
