00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:21,440
Reading classics by Zhu Ziqing.

609
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:23,380
I really need to apologize to him.

610
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,840
That's settled then.

611
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,120
Come in.

612
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:39,880
Why are you here?

613
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:41,040
If you're not feeling well,

614
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:42,640
you should rest more at home.

615
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:46,080
I just came to talk to you.

616
00:33:47,840 --> 00:33:48,840
I've resigned.

617
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,920
But I'll find a new job soon,

618
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:51,960
work hard to earn money

619
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:54,160
and compensate you for all your losses.

620
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:55,880
Haven't I already told you?

621
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,330
I'm the one who owes you.

622
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:00,000
You owe me emotionally,

623
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,560
but not professionally.

624
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:03,640
Let's keep things separate.

625
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:07,560
I wanted you to take on this auto show project

626
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:09,650
to help you out and make it up to you.

627
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:11,120
But now look what happened.

628
00:34:11,120 --> 00:34:13,380
It became a burden that cost you your job.

629
00:34:14,199 --> 00:34:16,280
I should be the one apologizing to you.

630
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:18,320
I came here today to apologize to you.

631
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:19,320
It's my fault.

632
00:34:19,520 --> 00:34:21,440
No, I'm the one who let you down.

633
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:23,040
I'm the one who wronged you.

634
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:24,699
No, when I say it's me, it's me.

635
00:34:24,719 --> 00:34:26,199
Fine, you let me down.

636
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,239
That's professionally,

637
00:34:28,239 --> 00:34:29,560
but not emotionally.

638
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:33,719
I know you've been good to me. I understand that.

639
00:34:33,719 --> 00:34:35,120
I'm not heartless.

640
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:38,080
But your company's losses are so significant this time.

641
00:34:38,080 --> 00:34:39,760
I definitely need to compensate you.

642
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,560
Stop mentioning this damn company.

643
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:42,360
If it weren't for this company

644
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:43,679
putting so much pressure on you,

645
00:34:43,679 --> 00:34:45,480
I might as well just shut it down.

646
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:46,480
Wait.

647
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:49,400
What's going on?

648
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,679
Everyone, pay attention. Come here.

649
00:34:51,679 --> 00:34:53,080
I have something to announce.

650
00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:54,040
Come over here.

651
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:57,450
Qin Gang.

652
00:34:58,120 --> 00:35:00,160
There's no need to joke about something like this.

653
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:01,600
This isn't child's play.

654
00:35:02,640 --> 00:35:04,160
I now officially announce.

655
00:35:04,160 --> 00:35:05,290
Starting tomorrow,

656
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:07,600
our dealership will be closed.

657
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:12,480
All personnel and financial matters

658
00:35:13,080 --> 00:35:14,280
need to be handled immediately.

659
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,520
Pay the compensations that are due

660
00:35:15,520 --> 00:35:17,580
and distribute all remaining funds.

661
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,120
Um,

662
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,680
I'm wondering if you're just

663
00:35:21,680 --> 00:35:22,940
joking with everyone?

664
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:24,360
I'm not joking.

665
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:29,360
I'm serious.

666
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:31,280
Is this really necessary?

667
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:32,400
Yes, it is.

668
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:36,600
Xinxin, from now on,

669
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:39,160
anything that makes you unhappy

670
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:41,040
is my enemy.

671
00:35:45,960 --> 00:35:48,160
Come with me to the finance department.

672
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:53,080
Xinxin.

673
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:54,680
Xinxin.

674
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:56,520
Why is this happening?

675
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:58,200
The business was doing fine and suddenly it's closed.

676
00:35:58,200 --> 00:35:59,520
I don't know either.

677
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:02,960
I'm completely confused right now.

678
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:05,580
Look, I was about to close several deals.

679
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:07,440
This... you...

680
00:36:07,640 --> 00:36:09,240
Is this good news or bad news?

681
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:15,800
You're really going all out this time.

682
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:19,400
The company is only closed for a couple of days.

683
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,640
I can still manage.

684
00:36:21,040 --> 00:36:23,100
I have enough for this small expense.

685
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:27,340
I'm just afraid Wan Xinxin won't appreciate it.

686
00:36:28,120 --> 00:36:31,000
Yes, she's so stubborn.

687
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:35,530
She needs something earth-shattering to be convinced.

688
00:36:36,680 --> 00:36:37,520
But I hope this time,

689
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:38,920
she'll take the bait.

690
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,440
Otherwise,

691
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:42,130
I'm really out of patience.

692
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:46,040
Oh right, what about Jiang Kaiyang?

693
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,200
I wonder if that idiot

694
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:49,930
has managed to get the job done.

695
00:36:50,200 --> 00:36:51,280
Is he capable?

696
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:56,680
I asked him to have a heart-to-heart with Hua Ming.

697
00:37:03,600 --> 00:37:05,800
I'm sorry. I was planning

698
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:08,120
to take us somewhere else,

699
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:10,840
but I realized this matter is urgent.

700
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:11,760
It's fine. This is good.

701
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:13,200
We'll have to make do with our staff cafeteria.

702
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:14,960
It's perfectly fine.

703
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,160
Where should I begin?

704
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,840
This lady,

705
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:22,320
things were better before she showed up.

706
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,520
As soon as she arrived, Mr. Qin

707
00:37:23,520 --> 00:37:25,800
took his anger out on the company.

708
00:37:26,040 --> 00:37:29,080
He thinks the company is causing her trouble,

709
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:31,200
so he simply decided to close the store.

710
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:34,240
So you want me to beg Wan Xinxin

711
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:36,160
to persuade Qin Gang?

712
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:39,840
Beg? Absolutely, brother.

713
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:41,960
Just think about it.

714
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:44,980
It wasn't easy for me to find this job. Not at all.

715
00:37:45,080 --> 00:37:47,280
This 4S dealership is a cushy position.

716
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:49,480
My current salary

717
00:37:49,640 --> 00:37:51,720
is double what I made at my previous job.

718
00:37:51,720 --> 00:37:53,920
Look, if he closes the store,

719
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:55,880
my livelihood is gone.

720
00:37:56,680 --> 00:37:58,000
At my age,

721
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:00,280
going around for job interviews,

722
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:02,080
wouldn't that be embarrassing?

723
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,200
Don't you think?

724
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:05,120
I'm also sitting at home without a proper job.

725
00:38:05,120 --> 00:38:06,180
You're different.

726
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:08,480
You're a respected doctor with substantial savings.

727
00:38:08,480 --> 00:38:11,000
You don't need to worry about supporting a family.

728
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:13,060
I have children studying abroad too.

729
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:15,740
I'm sorry, I wasn't aware of that.

730
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:17,620
What I mainly wanted to say is that

731
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,200
my wife

732
00:38:19,600 --> 00:38:22,360
will start acting up in just a few days.

733
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:24,440
It can't be that bad.

734
00:38:24,440 --> 00:38:26,040
It is. She's always wanted to

735
00:38:26,080 --> 00:38:27,840
rise up and be the one in charge.

736
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:30,170
Brother, you invited me for lunch,

737
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,560
can you be honest with me?

738
00:38:33,160 --> 00:38:35,440
Is Qin Gang really closing the store

739
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:37,060
because of Wan Xinxin?

740
00:38:38,120 --> 00:38:39,280
I think it's true.

741
00:38:39,680 --> 00:38:41,140
Let me show you something.

742
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:46,080
Take a look.

743
00:38:46,200 --> 00:38:46,760
What's this?

744
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:47,760
The account book.

745
00:38:50,160 --> 00:38:50,720
Look.

746
00:38:51,200 --> 00:38:53,260
I brought back all the account books.

747
00:38:53,720 --> 00:38:55,040
This means that

748
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,600
after organizing these things,

749
00:38:57,680 --> 00:38:59,610
I'll probably take some dividends

750
00:39:00,040 --> 00:39:01,360
and just stay at home.

751
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:07,100
The financial deficit is quite serious.

752
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:09,600
Wait, isn't your company profitable?

753
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:11,600
Profitable? It should be making money.

754
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,660
Look, our salaries

755
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:15,040
have basically never been delayed.

756
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:18,560
But there seems to be some issues with these books.

757
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:21,040
Well, I don't know about other things.

758
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,040
Dr. Hua.

759
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:23,480
I'd like to toast you.

760
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:30,440
Please help your sister.

761
00:39:30,720 --> 00:39:32,050
Look, I don't have a job,

762
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:34,820
and your brother-in-law might lose his too.

763
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:35,640
No, sis.

764
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:38,260
Brother-in-law is just unemployed at most.

765
00:39:38,560 --> 00:39:40,480
Don't nitpick, my dear.

766
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:44,640
I was there when he closed the store.

767
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:45,600
Couldn't stop him at all.

768
00:39:45,600 --> 00:39:47,960
I don't know how to help.

769
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,890
He just cares about your feelings.

770
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:53,000
If you feel better and get over this,

771
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,120
he won't be so stubborn anymore.

772
00:39:56,520 --> 00:39:58,640
Listen, go talk to him quickly.

773
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:00,080
Tell him to reopen the business.

774
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:01,880
He'll definitely listen to you.

775
00:40:02,360 --> 00:40:04,440
How would my persuasion work?

776
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,920
What can I say about you?

777
00:40:08,120 --> 00:40:10,000
You really don't know how good you have it.

778
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,530
What's wrong with Qin Gang?

779
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:13,920
He knows how to repent now.

780
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:15,920
Just give him a chance.

781
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:18,760
A prodigal son who returns is worth more than gold.

782
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:19,890
He's good-looking,

783
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:21,200
wealthy,

784
00:40:21,600 --> 00:40:23,730
where else could you find such a catch?

785
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:26,540
Just for your brother-in-law's job,

786
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:28,800
you're willing to sacrifice me?

787
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,840
Didn't you just call him a prodigal son?

788
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:33,040
And now you're pushing me into the fire.

789
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:36,660
You two should get back together anyway.

790
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,900
After all, you have a child together.

791
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:41,360
I only agree to see him because of our child.

792
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:44,290
Without the child, I wouldn't even acknowledge him.

793
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,130
The child isn't a reason at all.

794
00:40:46,240 --> 00:40:48,040
Fine, I won't say anything else,

795
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:50,280
but you must help with this job situation.

796
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,560
Mr. Qin closed his business because of you.

797
00:40:52,560 --> 00:40:55,000
You're acting like nothing happened. That's not right.

798
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:55,880
No,

799
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:57,800
I need to think about it.

800
00:40:58,360 --> 00:41:00,420
I need to figure out what to say to him.

801
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:01,960
Really?

802
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:03,840
Alright, take your time.

803
00:41:04,040 --> 00:41:05,840
I'll go get your brother-in-law's phone first.

804
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:06,840
Think it through.

805
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:07,760
Sis.

806
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,320
Have some water before you go.

807
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:10,240
No need for water.

808
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:11,700
Just think about it, okay?

809
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:23,370
They made you the mediator.

810
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,240
Exactly.

811
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,540
But thinking about it,

812
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:30,060
I do share some responsibility for this.

813
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,320
Wan Xinxin, are you okay?

814
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:34,480
Can you stop being so naive?

815
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:36,360
This has nothing to do with you.

816
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,800
How is it not related to me?

817
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:42,400
He closed the shop because of me, didn't he?

818
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,530
Your brother-in-law Jiang

819
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:46,560
has account books that I've seen.

820
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:48,680
His shop was already failing completely.

821
00:41:48,680 --> 00:41:50,320
He was losing money and just hanging on.

822
00:41:50,320 --> 00:41:52,320
The car show just gave him an excuse

823
00:41:52,640 --> 00:41:54,040
to save face. That's all.

824
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,540
You've seen the books?

825
00:41:58,480 --> 00:41:59,240
I don't believe it.

826
00:41:59,240 --> 00:42:01,000
When I was with him,

827
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,360
his shop was always profitable.

828
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:03,760
How could it be in the red?

829
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:06,370
Maybe it's just been a rough patch lately.

830
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:08,480
Wan Xinxin, haven't you always said

831
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:10,040
that experience counts for something, right?

832
00:42:10,040 --> 00:42:11,040
Aren't I older than you?

833
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:12,920
Shouldn't you trust my judgment?

